  364.     | Pexp_function pel -> sub.cases sub pel

  367.     | Pexp_match (e, pel) ->
  368.         sub.expr sub e; sub.cases sub pel

  370.     | Pexp_tuple el -> List.iter (sub.expr sub) el
  371.     | Pexp_construct (lid, arg) ->
  372.         iter_loc sub lid; iter_opt (sub.expr sub) arg
  373.     | Pexp_variant (_lab, eo) ->
  374.         iter_opt (sub.expr sub) eo
  375.     | Pexp_record (l, eo) ->
  376.         List.iter (iter_tuple (iter_loc sub) (sub.expr sub)) l;
  377.         iter_opt (sub.expr sub) eo
  378.     | Pexp_field (e, lid) ->

  383.     | Pexp_array el -> List.iter (sub.expr sub) el
  384.     | Pexp_ifthenelse (e1, e2, e3) ->

  386.         iter_opt (sub.expr sub) e3
  387.     | Pexp_sequence (e1, e2) ->
  388.         sub.expr sub e1; sub.expr sub e2
  389.     | Pexp_while (e1, e2) ->
  390.         sub.expr sub e1; sub.expr sub e2
  391.     | Pexp_for (p, e1, e2, _d, e3) ->
  392.         sub.pat sub p; sub.expr sub e1; sub.expr sub e2;
  393.         sub.expr sub e3
  394.     | Pexp_coerce (e, t1, t2) ->
  395.         sub.expr sub e; iter_opt (sub.typ sub) t1;
  396.         sub.typ sub t2
  397.     | Pexp_constraint (e, t) ->
  398.         sub.expr sub e; sub.typ sub t
  399.     | Pexp_send (e, _s) -> sub.expr sub e
  400.     | Pexp_new lid -> iter_loc sub lid
  401.     | Pexp_setinstvar (s, e) ->
  402.         iter_loc sub s; sub.expr sub e
  403.     | Pexp_override sel ->
  404.         List.iter (iter_tuple (iter_loc sub) (sub.expr sub)) sel
  405.     | Pexp_letmodule (s, me, e) ->
  406.         iter_loc sub s; sub.module_expr sub me;
  407.         sub.expr sub e
  408.     | Pexp_letexception (cd, e) ->
  409.         sub.extension_constructor sub cd;
  410.         sub.expr sub e
  411.     | Pexp_assert e -> sub.expr sub e
  412.     | Pexp_lazy e -> sub.expr sub e
  413.     | Pexp_poly (e, t) ->
  414.         sub.expr sub e; iter_opt (sub.typ sub) t
  415.     | Pexp_object cls -> sub.class_structure sub cls
  416.     | Pexp_newtype (_s, e) -> sub.expr sub e
  417.     | Pexp_pack me -> sub.module_expr sub me
  418.     | Pexp_open (o, e) ->
  419.         sub.open_declaration sub o; sub.expr sub e
  420.     | Pexp_letop {let_; ands; body} ->
  421.         sub.binding_op sub let_;
  422.         List.iter (sub.binding_op sub) ands;
  423.         sub.expr sub body

  425.     | Pexp_unreachable -> ()

  435. module P = struct

  438. ‌  let iter sub {ppat_desc = desc; ppat_loc = loc; ppat_attributes = attrs} =
  439.     sub.location sub loc;
  440.     sub.attributes sub attrs;
  441.     match desc with
  442.     | Ppat_any -> ()
  443.     | Ppat_var s -> iter_loc sub s
  444.     | Ppat_alias (p, s) -> sub.pat sub p; iter_loc sub s
  445.     | Ppat_constant _ -> ()
  446.     | Ppat_interval _ -> ()
  447.     | Ppat_tuple pl -> List.iter (sub.pat sub) pl
  448.     | Ppat_construct (l, p) ->
  449.         iter_loc sub l;
  450.         iter_opt
  451.           (fun (vl,p) ->
  452.             List.iter (iter_loc sub) vl;
  453.             sub.pat sub p)
  454.           p
  455.     | Ppat_variant (_l, p) -> iter_opt (sub.pat sub) p
  456.     | Ppat_record (lpl, _cf) ->
  457.         List.iter (iter_tuple (iter_loc sub) (sub.pat sub)) lpl
  458.     | Ppat_array pl -> List.iter (sub.pat sub) pl
  459.     | Ppat_or (p1, p2) -> sub.pat sub p1; sub.pat sub p2
  460.     | Ppat_constraint (p, t) ->
  461.         sub.pat sub p; sub.typ sub t
  462.     | Ppat_type s -> iter_loc sub s
  463.     | Ppat_lazy p -> sub.pat sub p
  464.     | Ppat_unpack s -> iter_loc sub s
  465.     | Ppat_exception p -> sub.pat sub p
  466.     | Ppat_extension x -> sub.extension sub x
  467.     | Ppat_open (lid, p) ->
  468.         iter_loc sub lid; sub.pat sub p

  470. end

  472. module CE = struct
  473.   (* Value expressions for the class language *)

  475. ‌  let iter sub {pcl_loc = loc; pcl_desc = desc; pcl_attributes = attrs} =
  476.     sub.location sub loc;
  477.     sub.attributes sub attrs;
  478.     match desc with
  479.     | Pcl_constr (lid, tys) ->
  480.         iter_loc sub lid; List.iter (sub.typ sub) tys
  481.     | Pcl_structure s ->
  482.         sub.class_structure sub s
  483.     | Pcl_fun (_lab, e, p, ce) ->
  484.         iter_opt (sub.expr sub) e;
  485.         sub.pat sub p;
  486.         sub.class_expr sub ce
  487.     | Pcl_apply (ce, l) ->
  488.         sub.class_expr sub ce;
  489.         List.iter (iter_snd (sub.expr sub)) l
  490.     | Pcl_let (_r, vbs, ce) ->
  491.         List.iter (sub.value_binding sub) vbs;
  492.         sub.class_expr sub ce
  493.     | Pcl_constraint (ce, ct) ->
  494.         sub.class_expr sub ce; sub.class_type sub ct
  495.     | Pcl_extension x -> sub.extension sub x
  496.     | Pcl_open (o, e) ->
  497.         sub.open_description sub o; sub.class_expr sub e

  499. ‌  let iter_kind sub = function
  500.     | Cfk_concrete (_o, e) -> sub.expr sub e
  501.     | Cfk_virtual t -> sub.typ sub t

  503. ‌  let iter_field sub {pcf_desc = desc; pcf_loc = loc; pcf_attributes = attrs} =
  504.     sub.location sub loc;
  505.     sub.attributes sub attrs;
  506.     match desc with
  507.     | Pcf_inherit (_o, ce, _s) -> sub.class_expr sub ce
  508.     | Pcf_val (s, _m, k) -> iter_loc sub s; iter_kind sub k
  509.     | Pcf_method (s, _p, k) ->
  510.         iter_loc sub s; iter_kind sub k
  511.     | Pcf_constraint (t1, t2) ->
  512.         sub.typ sub t1; sub.typ sub t2
  513.     | Pcf_initializer e -> sub.expr sub e
  514.     | Pcf_attribute x -> sub.attribute sub x
  515.     | Pcf_extension x -> sub.extension sub x

  517. ‌  let iter_structure sub {pcstr_self; pcstr_fields} =
  518.     sub.pat sub pcstr_self;
  519.     List.iter (sub.class_field sub) pcstr_fields

  521. ‌  let class_infos sub f {pci_virt = _; pci_params = pl; pci_name; pci_expr;
  522.                          pci_loc; pci_attributes} =
  523.     List.iter (iter_fst (sub.typ sub)) pl;
  524.     iter_loc sub pci_name;
  525.     f pci_expr;
  526.     sub.location sub pci_loc;
  527.     sub.attributes sub pci_attributes
  528. end

  530. (* Now, a generic AST mapper, to be extended to cover all kinds and
  531.    cases of the OCaml grammar.  The default behavior of the mapper is
  532.    the identity. *)

  534. ‌let default_iterator =
  535.   {
  536.     structure = (fun this l -> List.iter (this.structure_item this) l);
  537.     structure_item = M.iter_structure_item;
  538.     module_expr = M.iter;
  539.     signature = (fun this l -> List.iter (this.signature_item this) l);
  540.     signature_item = MT.iter_signature_item;
  541.     module_type = MT.iter;
  542.     with_constraint = MT.iter_with_constraint;
  543.     class_declaration =
  544.       (fun this -> CE.class_infos this (this.class_expr this));
  545.     class_expr = CE.iter;
  546.     class_field = CE.iter_field;
  547.     class_structure = CE.iter_structure;
  548.     class_type = CT.iter;
  549.     class_type_field = CT.iter_field;
  550.     class_signature = CT.iter_signature;
  551.     class_type_declaration =
  552.       (fun this -> CE.class_infos this (this.class_type this));
  553.     class_description =
  554.       (fun this -> CE.class_infos this (this.class_type this));
  555.     type_declaration = T.iter_type_declaration;
  556.     type_kind = T.iter_type_kind;
  557.     typ = T.iter;
  558.     row_field = T.row_field;
  559.     object_field = T.object_field;
  560.     type_extension = T.iter_type_extension;
  561.     type_exception = T.iter_type_exception;
  562.     extension_constructor = T.iter_extension_constructor;
  563.     value_description =
  564.       (fun this {pval_name; pval_type; pval_prim = _; pval_loc;
  565.                  pval_attributes} ->
  566.         iter_loc this pval_name;
  567.         this.typ this pval_type;
  568.         this.location this pval_loc;
  569.         this.attributes this pval_attributes;
  570.       );

  572.     pat = P.iter;
  573.     expr = E.iter;
  574.     binding_op = E.iter_binding_op;

  576.     module_declaration =
  577.       (fun this {pmd_name; pmd_type; pmd_attributes; pmd_loc} ->
  578.          iter_loc this pmd_name;
  579.          this.module_type this pmd_type;
  580.          this.location this pmd_loc;
  581.          this.attributes this pmd_attributes;
  582.       );

  584.     module_substitution =
  585.       (fun this {pms_name; pms_manifest; pms_attributes; pms_loc} ->
  586.          iter_loc this pms_name;
  587.          iter_loc this pms_manifest;
  588.          this.location this pms_loc;
  589.          this.attributes this pms_attributes;
  590.       );

  592.     module_type_declaration =
  593.       (fun this {pmtd_name; pmtd_type; pmtd_attributes; pmtd_loc} ->
  594.          iter_loc this pmtd_name;
  595.          iter_opt (this.module_type this) pmtd_type;
  596.          this.location this pmtd_loc;
  597.          this.attributes this pmtd_attributes;
  598.       );

  600.     module_binding =
  601.       (fun this {pmb_name; pmb_expr; pmb_attributes; pmb_loc} ->
  602.          iter_loc this pmb_name; this.module_expr this pmb_expr;
  603.          this.location this pmb_loc;
  604.          this.attributes this pmb_attributes;
  605.       );

  607.     open_declaration =
  608.       (fun this {popen_expr; popen_override = _; popen_attributes; popen_loc} ->
  609.          this.module_expr this popen_expr;
  610.          this.location this popen_loc;
  611.          this.attributes this popen_attributes
  612.       );

  614.     open_description =
  615.       (fun this {popen_expr; popen_override = _; popen_attributes; popen_loc} ->
  616.          iter_loc this popen_expr;
  617.          this.location this popen_loc;
  618.          this.attributes this popen_attributes
  619.       );


  622.     include_description =
  623.       (fun this {pincl_mod; pincl_attributes; pincl_loc} ->
  624.          this.module_type this pincl_mod;
  625.          this.location this pincl_loc;
  626.          this.attributes this pincl_attributes
  627.       );

  629.     include_declaration =
  630.       (fun this {pincl_mod; pincl_attributes; pincl_loc} ->
  631.          this.module_expr this pincl_mod;
  632.          this.location this pincl_loc;
  633.          this.attributes this pincl_attributes
  634.       );


  637.     value_binding =
  638.       (fun this {pvb_pat; pvb_expr; pvb_attributes; pvb_loc; pvb_constraint} ->
  639.          this.pat this pvb_pat;
  640.          this.expr this pvb_expr;
  641.          Option.iter (function
  642.              | Parsetree.Pvc_constraint {locally_abstract_univars=vars; typ} ->
  643.                  List.iter (iter_loc this) vars;
  644.                  this.typ this typ
  645.              | Pvc_coercion { ground; coercion } ->
  646.                  Option.iter (this.typ this) ground;
  647.                  this.typ this coercion;
  648.            ) pvb_constraint;
  649.          this.location this pvb_loc;
  650.          this.attributes this pvb_attributes
  651.       );


  654.     constructor_declaration =
  655.       (fun this {pcd_name; pcd_vars; pcd_args;
  656.                  pcd_res; pcd_loc; pcd_attributes} ->
  657.          iter_loc this pcd_name;
  658.          List.iter (iter_loc this) pcd_vars;
  659.          T.iter_constructor_arguments this pcd_args;
  660.          iter_opt (this.typ this) pcd_res;
  661.          this.location this pcd_loc;
  662.          this.attributes this pcd_attributes
  663.       );

  665.     label_declaration =
  666.       (fun this {pld_name; pld_type; pld_loc; pld_mutable = _; pld_attributes}->
  667.          iter_loc this pld_name;
  668.          this.typ this pld_type;
  669.          this.location this pld_loc;
  670.          this.attributes this pld_attributes
  671.       );

  673.     cases = (fun this l -> List.iter (this.case this) l);
  674.     case =
  675.       (fun this {pc_lhs; pc_guard; pc_rhs} ->
  676.          this.pat this pc_lhs;
  677.          iter_opt (this.expr this) pc_guard;
  678.          this.expr this pc_rhs
  679.       );

  681.     location = (fun _this _l -> ());

  683.     extension = (fun this (s, e) -> iter_loc this s; this.payload this e);
  684.     attribute = (fun this a ->
  685.       iter_loc this a.attr_name;
  686.       this.payload this a.attr_payload;
  687.       this.location this a.attr_loc
  688.     );
  689.     attributes = (fun this l -> List.iter (this.attribute this) l);
  690.     payload =
  691.       (fun this -> function
  692.          | PStr x -> this.structure this x
  693.          | PSig x -> this.signature this x
  694.          | PTyp x -> this.typ this x
  695.          | PPat (x, g) -> this.pat this x; iter_opt (this.expr this) g
  696.       );
  697.   }
